2:34 pm case called. Defendant Joshua A Breezee in court.  Steven Paul Anderson appeared for the State of Wisconsin.  Court questions parties. Resolution reached and entered into the record. Defendant advised of right to expunge DNA record through the Department of Justice. Appeal Rights Given.
